messages.msgSnippet: I thought this looked funny, but didnt say anything.  Read my signature. I often do this. Yesterday I was looking for a new name for our new dog, whose name
messages.messageBody:
I thought this looked funny, but didnt' say
anything. Read my signature.

I often do this.

Yesterday I was looking for a new name for
our new dog, whose name is freckles. My
daughter wants Hermoine. So I went to a
bunch of websites, looking at names and also
looking to see what Hermoine means. It
wasnt' until the end of the day that I
thought--hm, what if I'm spelling it wrong.
Hermione. Oops. About 2 minutes later I got
a note from Dar, saying sweetly, Joylyn, are
you mispelling it? LOL. Uh, YES! oh well.

I think we are going with Addie, btw. for a
name.

And one time I said I was a slut when I meant
clutz.

oops.

Joylyn
